--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project structure:

src/main/java:
	com.config:
		Config.properties
		
	com.pages:
		LandingPage.java
		CommunityForumPage.java
		UnansweredPage.java
		UnansweredSearchPage.java
		
	com.testdata:
		testdata.xlsx	
			
	com.utility:
		Config.java
		ConfigReader.java
		ExcelReader.ja
		ExtentReporterManager.java
		Utility.java
		
src/test/java:
		apphooks:
		ApplicationHooks.java
	
		communityforum_1_stepdefinition:
		CommunityForum_1_Step.java
		
		communityforum_2_stepdefinitions:
		CommunityForum_2_Step.java	
		
		excel_stepdefinitions:
		Excel_Step.java
		
		testrunner:
		CommunityForum_1_TestRunner.java
		CommunityForum_1_TestRunner.java
		Excel_TestRunner.java
			
src/main/resources:
	ReadMe
						
src/test/resources:
	features folder
		CommunityForum_1.feature	
		CommunityForum_2.feature
		Excel.feature

drivers folder:
	chromedriver.exe
	
screenshots folder:
	file.png	

Extent folder:	
	extent_reports	
	
pom.xml			
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project creation sequence:

Create maven project
Add the dependencies in pom.xml
Maven project will have 4 sections by default(if not then create them):
	src/main/java
	src/main/resources
	src/test/java
	src/test/resources

Create the required packages, classes, files in them as per below sequence:

Step 1 --> Create Feature file
Step 2 --> Create Config.java
Step 3 --> Create Config.properties
Step 4 --> Create ConfigReader.java
Step 5 --> Create Utility.java
Step 6 --> Create LandingPage.java
Step 7 --> Create CommunityForumPage.java
Step 8 --> Create UnansweredPage.java
Step 9 --> Create UnansweredSearchPage.java
Step 10 --> Create ApplicationHooks.java
Step 11 --> Create LandingPageStep.java
Step 12 --> Create CommunityForum_Step.java
Step 13 --> Create Excel_Step.java
Step 14 --> Create CommunityForum_TestRunner.java
Step 15 --> Create Excel_TestRunner.java

Create the drivers folder and keep driver in it
Create the screenshots folder to keep screenshots in it
Create the extent folder
Run the tests by using Test class(individual test class) or pom.xml

See the reports in test-output folder(created by testng)
See the reports in target folder(created by maven)
